thread.title: Brett Green
thread.title_full: Mystery Tackle Box reviewed by Brett Green

author: Brett Green
title: Brett Green
text: I have only received three of the Mystery Tackle Box Pro boxes, but so far it is very much so worth the money! You get a great selection of quality baits for a low price. It's great to try new baits and lures without having to do research because MTB does it for you. You get to try things you may never think of trying. It's an awesome program!
